# Secrets. Plaintext env never lives in git: .env.prod is your local source for the box secrets and .env is dev/the box's decrypted runtime file. The ENCRYPTED .env.sops IS committed (SOPS+age) — it is not matched by the patterns below.
.env
.env.prod

# Box-local deploy state, written by deploy/deploy.sh inside the box's clone.
.last_good_tag
.env.tmp

# Agents
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
.agent/